title: Christmas at Rao's-Celebration of Family
description:
Rao' is an Italian restaurant in New York City from many years ago. If you had dinner there during Christmas-time these are the song you would expect to hear. A real treat. - Big Papi
-
-
-
By Irvin Goodman HALL OF FAMEVINE VOICE
Brand new CD with 16 tracks of songs loved by all, by the original artists. These are favorites performed at Rao's Italian Restaurant in New York City, that have been played for years at holiday time. To get into the holiday spirit, this is a must. It features: Its The Most Wonderful Time of the Year by Andy Williams, The Christmas Song by Mel Torme, Ave Maria by Michael Amante, Buon Natale by The Four Coins, Winter Wonderland by Tony Bennett, Christmas Auld Lang Syne by Bobby Darin and Have Yourself A Merry Little Christmas by Jonny Maestro, and more. Just hearing these favorites instantly put me in a holiday mood. It's a winner. Enjoy !!
